      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor said it's super important to keep the levels steady in my blood so i don't have a stroke or something. if i only take one now and wait until tomorrow morning for the next one, won't my levels drop too low in between? i'm worried that's more dangerous than just taking two now to stay in the safe range.",
